text: Swan 43-127 Trouper The Swan 43 Holland is the second Swan 43 model this time designed by Ron Holland and built by Nautor's Swan and first launched in 1985 to 1990 with 28 built. They were numbered from 101 to distinguish them from the earlier S&S; 43\. ==External links== * Nautor Swan * Designers Official Website ==References== Category:Sailing yachts Category:Keelboats Category:1980s sailboat type designs Category:Sailboat types built by Nautor Swan Category:Sailboat type designs by Ron Holland
